    "title": "SeaKing J07 Fiberglass Fillet Table (L27.6\" x W16.5\")",
    "body_html": "<div data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"ProductItem-details-excerpt\" data-content-field=\"excerpt\" id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1686881405683_441\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Sea King SK-J07</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>The SeaKing SK-J07 and SK-K08 boast a sophisticated and durable design, featuring a sleek </span><span>appearance complemented by a spacious knife tray and storage sink. Available in white or black </span><span>gelcoat finishes, these fillet tables are meticulously handcrafted using premium composite materials, </span><span>including a UV resistant PE plastic cutting board for lasting performance on the water. Designed to </span><span>combine elegance with functionality, these fillet tables are perfect for anglers seeking a stylish yet </span><span>robust solution for their fishing needs. </span></p>\n<ul></ul>\n</div>",
